---
title: Cheesy Capsicum Chicken & Herby Root Veg with Garlic Butter Broccoli
description: Load up chicken breasts with flavour before baking them until golden and tender. Chargrilled capsicum relish and melted Cheddar combine to make a sensational topping that everyone will happily devour!

